ages\":{\"fallback\":{\"src\":\"/static/698144f5aa68b3eaecff631440ff1cdb/04d84/protocollo.png\",\"srcSet\":\"/static/698144f5aa68b3eaecff631440ff1cdb/5f49f/protocollo.png 236w,\\n/static/698144f5aa68b3eaecff631440ff1cdb/fbd60/protocollo.png 472w,\\n/static/698144f5aa68b3eaecff631440ff1cdb/04d84/protocollo.png 943w\",\"sizes\":\"(min-width: 943px) 943px, 100vw\"},\"sources\":[{\"srcSet\":\"/static/698144f5aa68b3eaecff631440ff1cdb/a03c0/protocollo.webp 236w,\\n/static/698144f5aa68b3eaecff631440ff1cdb/e024d/protocollo.webp 472w,\\n/static/698144f5aa68b3eaecff631440ff1cdb/16732/protocollo.webp 943w\",\"type\":\"image/webp\",\"sizes\":\"(min-width: 943px) 943px, 100vw\"}]},\"width\":943,\"height\":404.99999999999994},\"alt\":\"\",\"className\":\"aligncenter wp-image-1971 size-full inline-gatsby-image-wrapper\",\"data-wp-inline-image\":\"6\"}</script></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Ho guardato per curiosità la lista degli otto <a href=\"https://www.agid.gov.it/it/agenzia/difensore-civico-il-digitale/inviti-pa\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">inviti fatti alle Pubbliche Amministrazioni dal Difensore Digitale</a> nel periodo compreso tra il 10/05/2018 ed il 07/11/2018 e nessuno riguarda SPID.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.agid.gov.it/it/agenzia/difensore-civico-il-digitale/inviti-pa\"><div data-gatsby-image-wrapper=\"\" style=\"position:relative;overflow:hidden;display:inline-block;vertical-align:top\" class=\"gatsby-image-wrapper gatsby-image-wrapper-constrained aligncenter wp-image-1972 size-large inline-gatsby-image-wrapper\" data-reactroot=\"\"><div style=\"max-width:660px;display:block\"><img alt=\"\" role=\"presentation\" aria-hidden=\"true\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml;charset=utf-8,%3Csvg height=&#x27;353&#x27; width=&#x27;660&#x27; xmlns=&#x27;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#x27; version=&#x27;1.1&#x27;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" style=\"max-width:100%;display:block;position:static\"/></div><div aria-hidden=\"true\" data-placeholder-image=\"\" style=\"height:100%;left:0;position:abso